## âš™ï¸ Performance Snapshot

| Task                     |    Python    |   Rust (pyO3)  |
|--------------------------|--------------|----------------|
| from_file                |    ~160â€¯ms   |     ~4 ms      |
| detect_silence           |    ~700 ms   |     ~17 ms     |
| detect_nonsilent         |    ~700 ms   |     ~17 ms     |
| split_on_silence         |    ~700 ms   |     ~17 ms     |
| detect_leading_silence   |    ~280 Î¼s   |     ~9 Î¼s      |

** audio duration 10s and sample rate 32,000 (~320,000 samples) **

> **Symphonia** provides native decoding, multi-format support, and fast performanceâ€”ideal for preprocessing pipelines like F5-TTS.


